         <h3><a name="children"></a>Children's Society Fashion Show, Thursday 25th June, 12.30 pm</h3>
        <p>Our annual Ploughman's Lunch, Fashion Show and Sale, with clothes from "Travelling Trends", will be held at All Saints' Church Hall at 12.30 pm on Thursday 25th June. After lunch provided by the Society, Travelling Trends will present a 45 - 60 minute show featuring a mixture of classic and fasionable lines to suit ladies of all ages and most sizes. The company boasts a constantly changing range of branded items as its wholesalers buy direct from manufacutreres who also supply popular high street stores and individual boutiques.</p>
        <p>After the show visitors wil have the opportunity to buy the clothes displayed most of which are offered for at least 50% less than their typical retail price!</p>
        <p>Tickets - priced Â£10, to include a glass of wine with lunch - must be purchased in advance to facilitate catering. Please do contact your local Children's Society committee member or ring or email me, Rachel Chadd, 020 8668 6769, <%= mail_to "rchad@tiscali.co.uk" %></p>
        </div><!-- col-md-10 -->
